
USAGE: spair white white black black

This command helps 4 players to set up a pair-go game.

Example:  spair tromp gege geek talby

This would give instructions to tromp, gege, geek, and talby on how to set up
a pair-go game.  tromp and gege are the White team, while geek and talby are
the black team.

NOTES: You must be one of the 4 players listed in the spair command.
       This command does *not* set up the matches, only provides instructions.

SEE ALSO: pair match

